sequenceDiagram
  participant PYNQ as PYNQ board_client
  participant PC as PC Server
  participant Store as JSONL records

  PYNQ->>PC: sensor_data
  PC->>Store: append sensor_data
  PC->>PC: classify sensor_data
  PC-->>PYNQ: sleep_result
  PC->>Store: append sleep_result
  PC->>PC: comfort_policy(sensor_data, sleep_result)
  PC-->>PYNQ: control_command
  PC->>Store: append control_command
  PYNQ->>PYNQ: validate and execute/skip command
  PYNQ->>PC: control_status
  PC->>Store: append control_status

